set.seed(999)
# 
mat = matrix(sample(18, 18), 3, 6)
rownames(mat) = paste0("S", 1:3)
colnames(mat) = paste0("E", 1:6)
head(mat)
##    E1 E2 E3 E4 E5 E6
## S1  4 14 13 17  5  2
## S2  7  1  6  8 12 15
## S3  9 10  3 16 11 18
# 
df = data.frame(from = rep(rownames(mat), times = ncol(mat)), #
                to = rep(colnames(mat), each = nrow(mat)), #
                value = as.vector(mat),#
                stringsAsFactors = FALSE)
head(df)
##   from to value
## 1   S1 E1     4
## 2   S2 E1     7
## 3   S3 E1     9
## 4   S1 E2    14
## 5   S2 E2     1
## 6   S3 E2    10
# chordDiagram
# 
chordDiagram(mat)

# 
circos.clear() 

# 
chordDiagram(df)

circos.clear()

# ordersectors
chordDiagram(mat, 
             order = c("S2", "S1", "E4", "E1", "S3", 
                       "E5", "E2", "E6", "E3"))

circos.clear()

# grid.colsectors
grid_col = c(S1 = "red", S2 = "green", S3 = "blue",
             E1 = "yellow", E2 = "pink", E3 = "orange", 
             E4 = "purple", E5 = "black", E6 = "grey")
# transparency
chordDiagram(mat, 
             grid.col = grid_col,
             transparency = 0.7)

circos.clear()

# collinks
col_mat = rand_color(length(mat), transparency = 0.5)
head(col_mat)
## [1] "#A4566980" "#91874C80" "#8E9BB680" "#C2D1BC80" "#48484980" "#D1ACBD80"
chordDiagram(mat, 
             col = col_mat)

circos.clear()

# link.borderlink.ltylink.lwdlinks
chordDiagram(mat, 
             link.border = "red",
             link.lty = 2,
             link.lwd = 2)

circos.clear()

# annotationTracksectorsc("name", "grid", "axis")
chordDiagram(mat, grid.col = grid_col, 
             annotationTrack = "grid" # gird
             ) 

chordDiagram(mat, grid.col = grid_col, 
             annotationTrack = c("name", "grid"), # 
             annotationTrackHeight = c(0.04, 0.02) # 
             )  

chordDiagram(mat, grid.col = grid_col, 
             annotationTrack = NULL) # 

circos.clear()

# circos.par
circos.par(clock.wise = FALSE, #
           start.degree = 60 #60
           )
chordDiagram(mat)

circos.clear()

#sectorgap
circos.par(gap.after = c("S1" = 5, "S2" = 8, "S3" = 15, 
                         "E1" = 5, "E2" = 10,"E3" = 5, 
                         "E4" = 3, "E5" = 5, "E6" = 15))
chordDiagram(mat)

circos.clear()
